snippet.title: The Cycle - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Cycle is YAGER's next game project that is currently in Alpha Testing. 

If you would like to join our testing community, please go to: https://thecycle.game and fill out the Alpha Tester application form.

Next tests are on:
- November 15th-17th
- December 14th-16th

•    Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/product/thecycle 
•    Official website: https://thecycle.game
•    Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TheCycleGame/ 
•    Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/thecyclegame/
•    Twitter: https://twitter.com/thecyclegame
•    Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/thecyclegame
•    Discord:  https://discordapp.com/invite/eCHCnRK
